Package: araponga
Title: Estimating 3D Angles from 2D Landmarks
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2026-03-19
Authors@R: 
    person("João C T", "Menezes", "", "jocateme@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4156-2934"))
Description: This package allows users to extract 3D orientations
    (left/right, up/down) of an object based on 2D image coordinates of
    two landmarks and the (approximate) elevation angle between camera and
    object.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    arrow,
    dplyr,
    graphics,
    rlang
Suggests: 
    curl,
    httr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
